    "Metadata": {
        "Id": "5f82ba32-fa40-4387-8b83-589a81c7e926",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "Devil&apos;s Wingman IV - Big Diederik Energy",
        "Location": "LOCATION_EDGY_FOX",
        "PublicId": "129180468938",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/edgy/mission_fox/scene_fox_contractcreation.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository ae43204d-2960-4aed-99dd-8f18fca05cd5).Image",
        "Description": "Due to you, 47, our client and his lady are now engaged. He wants one last wild night, however, and his best man has reached out to us to ensure that Diederik Van Der Heijeden is able to DJ at his friend’s bachelor party. Heijeden is currently the celebrity DJ of Club Hölle in Berlin, so you’ll need to make sure he leaves that position. Suspicion of kidnapping and murder should facilitate his availability and deflate his asking price. Oh, a motorcycle would make an excellent wedding gift.",
